  "meta": {
    "table": "9-8",
    "title": "Residual Nitrogen Time Table for Repetitive Air Dives (Surface Interval Credit + Residual Nitrogen Time, read in two passes)",
    "source": "US Navy Diving Manual Rev 7 Change A (2018)",
    "source_url": "https://www.divetable.info/workshop/USN_Rev7_Tables.pdf",
    "cross_check_url": "https://www.uhms.org/images/MEDFAQs/February-2017/2nd/US_DIVING_MANUALREV7_TT2A.pdf",
    "verified": false,
    "coverage_notes": "Full USN Rev 7 Table 9-8 (page 9-64). PASS 1 (surface_interval_pass): the diagonal Surface Interval Credit block for ALL starting groups A-O plus Z. Each starting group's surface-interval windows (min) tile contiguously from 10 min upward down to group A; the final row (new_group '*') marks intervals longer than the tabulated max, after which the next dive is NOT a repetitive dive. Window times were transcribed from the manual's H:MM cells and converted to whole minutes; contiguity (no gaps/overlaps, each group reaching A) was verified programmatically. PASS 2 (rnt_pass): the Residual Nitrogen Time grid for end-of-SI groups A-O plus Z at every air-ladder depth 25-190 fsw. All 25-190 cells are numeric EXCEPT the two '\u2020' cells at 25 fsw / groups O and Z (manual footnote: 'read down to the 30 fsw repetitive dive depth' substitute rule) which are DELIBERATELY OMITTED rather than mis-encoded as '**' (which would emit the wrong para 9-9.1 subpara-8 citation); the engine surfaces a clean 'no RNT cell seeded' warning for them. The manual's shallow depths 10/15/20 fsw (which contain genuine '**' undeterminable cells) are omitted to match the 9-7 ladder (25+). Transcribed by rendering page 9-64 at 300-500 DPI and mapping every cell to its column by coordinate; row 190 and the '\u2020' cells were additionally spot-checked against zoomed crops. Confidence: HIGH (coordinate-verified, surface-interval contiguity check passes, RNT depths are a subset of the air ladder). '**' = RNT undeterminable (para 9-9.1 subpara 8); no '**' cells fall within the 25-190 range included here.",
    "unverified_warning": "Transcribed from US Navy Rev 7 references (2026-07-04); not yet cross-checked cell-by-cell against a physical manual \u2014 verify before any real use.",
    "min_credited_surface_interval_min": 10
  },
